author: skitching
msg: Fix a very nasty bug introduced by MYFACES-434. The delegate.release
method is only called intermittently, because there is a "return"
statement right in the middle of the large implementation of the release
function, and delegate.release is called outside of the finally method.
There is probably a better fix than this, but it should do for now.
